data.description: Wonderful Lake Home! Perfect for the Weekender, Vacationer or Empty Nester. Site built 2 bd., 2 bth., Stucco Home on 2 combined lots. Steel framing, tape and textured, freshly painted walls, tile floors in living room, dining area, kitchen and baths. New wall /wall carpet in both bedrooms. Beautiful hickory cabinets and tiled counter tops in the kitchen. All appliances stay including washer/dryer combo. Heat and cool with dual heat pumps. Truly an inviting home with its outdoor covered 13x13 patio, several trees for shade and plenty of eye catching sunsets. All fenced yard, great 2 space Carpot with attached 11x21 Workshop. Additional carport on lower lot. Need a big garage? This property has the room. Only one HOA fee. at 40.00 annually. The Club house has a lot to offer with large swimming pool, tennis court, shuffle board, putt-putt golf and lounge with free Wi-Fi for members, just to name a few.
